{"tid":657443,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟大學生幾時先會識點去廁所","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T15:12:13.000Z","uid":149662,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bbeb1bc24780cbfc5b0ac43ef602096cc94e95","tid":657443,"uid":149662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母最中意去廁所唔沖廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成撚日個廁格都係周圍都係尿<br />\n最誇張見過廁板都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入到大學但控制唔到自己屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係控制唔到就去尿兜屙<br />\n驚自己條撚太細俾人見到就坐低喺廁格屙，增加準成度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔小心屙到廁板，就自己攞張紙巾抹一抹返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成撚日想屙屎個廁格都好似中國啲廁所咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e2ea004bf27b61036d19d69a17712907c87104","tid":657443,"uid":73179,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"而家香港嘅大學=公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25795add19df7a67ea530a7edbaa88609d1c0e31","tid":657443,"uid":18735,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"你覺得依家香港嘅大學好多香港人讀？"},{"pid":"254baaa6715bf255bfd3283c5106e8b682c37b6e","tid":657443,"uid":4575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"蝗太多，不過香港人都係好少少"},{"pid":"7d9c15fec2452890badf70560ec38390691247a8","tid":657443,"uid":75193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:21:24.000Z","msg":"大學生有幾多本地人"},{"pid":"92de2deff437a4a90b3718a356ec7c494b23ac5d","tid":657443,"uid":149662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25795add19df7a67ea530a7edbaa88609d1c0e31","tid":657443,"uid":18735,"like":32,"di